This topic describes how to use SSH to connect to the Ops Manager VM or the BOSH Director VM.

## <a id="overview"></a> Overview

To troubleshoot your Ops Manager deployments successfully, you may need to SSH into the Ops Manager or BOSH Director VM.

After you successfully SSH into the Ops Manager VM, you can perform troubleshooting operations. For more information about troubleshooting, see [Advanced Troubleshooting with the BOSH CLI](./trouble-advanced.html).

